channel.title: Problem with making someone an admin
channel.description:
ok so my friend on the server "symphony x" has won the rights to be an admin. so i go into his player file, and for plaer rights i put "2-" and now he can't log in and it says he's already logged in
and on mopar it says for him " server is down" he clicks it again and it says "hes already logged in"
[code]ClientHandler: Accepted from localhost:4433 Client type: low memory version UserId: 11806057 symphony x is signing onto server. ClientHandler: Accepted from localhost:4434 Client type: low memory version UserId: 11806057 symphony x is signing onto server. [client-2-symphony x]: symphony x is already online. Did not save for symphony x ClientHandler: Client symphony x disconnected. ClientHandler: Accepted from localhost:4435 Client type: low memory version UserId: 11806057 symphony x is signing onto server. [client-2-symphony x]: symphony x is already online. ClientHandler: Accepted from localhost:4436 Client type: low memory version UserId: 11806057 symphony x is signing onto server. [client-3-symphony x]: symphony x is already online. Did not save for symphony x ClientHandler: Client symphony x disconnected. ClientHandler: Accepted from localhost:4437 Client type: low memory version UserId: 11806057 symphony x is signing onto server. [client-2-symphony x]: symphony x is already online. ClientHandler: Accepted from localhost:4438 Client type: low memory version UserId: 11806057 symphony x is signing onto server. [client-4-symphony x]: symphony x is already online. Did not save for symphony x ClientHandler: Client symphony x disconnected. Did not save for symphony x ClientHandler: Client symphony x disconnected. Did not save for symphony x ClientHandler: Client symphony x disconnected.[/code]
thats after trying to log in after a few trys
any help please?
